---
title: Chipotle Pork for Tacos
servings: 8
tags:
  - entres
---

Fry @onion{2}(sliced) in an #instant pot{}.

If the @pork{4%lb} is not in chunks (~3 inches), cut it into chunks.

Add the pork and @chipotle in adobo{7%oz}, @apple cider vinegar{0.25%cup}, @fish sauce{0.25%cup}, @garlic powder{1%tbsp}, @cumin{1%tbsp}(powder), @oregano{2%tbsp}(dry), @bay leaves{1%tsp}(powder), and @cacao{1%tsp}(powder) to the instant pot.

Cook on high pressure for ~{45%minutes}, allow natural release.
